<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>trademe.git</title>
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<style>
		* {
			box-sizing: border-box;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			font-family: Inter;
		}
		body {
			gap: 20px;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			/* align-items: center; */
			margin: auto;
			width: fit-content;
			justify-content: center;
			height: 100vh;
		}
		.steam-login {
			color: white;
			align-self: baseline;
			display:flex;
			border-radius: 12px;
			border: none;
			background: #79E283;
			transition: all 0.05s linear;
			align-items:center;
			padding:8px 9px;
			gap:20px
		}

		.steam-login:hover {
			cursor: pointer;
			background: #62b96b;
		}

		.steam-login:active {
			box-shadow: inset 0px 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
			transform: scale(0.95);
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<main style>
		<h1>bouncytorch's trading bot</h1>
		<p>
			<span style="color:#929292">whats this?:</span> an example trading bot, my portfolio project<br>
			<span style="color:#929292">how does it work?:</span> you pick items you want to trade me and the bot sends thou a trade request<br>
			<span style="color:#929292">do i get anything from it?:</span> no.<br>
			<span style="color:#929292">why?:</span> this is just a portfolio project not intended for practical use. <br>
			it's created for the sole purpose of showcasing my abilities as a backend/frontend engineer<br>
			and my ability to operate steam api. <b>i am not obligated to return the items you trade me.</b><br>
			if you do decide to trade me something tho, thank you for a charitable donation :)<br>
			<span style="color:#929292">what abilities does it showcase?:</span>
			<ol style="padding:0px 25px;">
				<li>my frontend skills (specifically react, css, js)</li>
				<li>steam api and steam bot tools solution</li>
				<li>cryptography (encryption of the config file)</li>
				<li>misc. backend skills (node.js)</li>
			</ol>
		</p>
	</main>
	<form action="/auth" method="post">
		<button class="steam-login" type="submit"><span style="font-size:15px">login with steam</span><img src="/steam.svg" alt=""></button>
	</form>
</body>
</html>